title: 2 Weeks Free! North Beach 1x1 Renovated, Walk to Wash Square Park
posting_body: ['*Promotion - 2 Weeks Free Rent!', 'Eat Pray Rent 28 Houston: North Beach 1/1 by RentingSF', 'RentingSF.co proudly presents North Beach original 1/1 with updated gourmet kitchen with island counter.', 'Make memorable meals and enjoy the good life at 28 Houston off Columbus.', "Let there be light in spacious mid-century modern apartment on this cul-de-sac located a quick walk from such renowned restaurants as Tony's Pizzeria Napoletana, Original Joe's & Victoria Bakery.", 'Walk to North Beach Library and Pool, St Peter &;; Paul Church, Washington Square and Aquatic Park.', 'Immediate occupancy.', 'Tails of the City pets Ok with Owner Approval.', 'RentingSF.co established 2004.', '* Eat pray rent this North Beach upscale update - Holy Cannoli !!', '* Mid century update with upscale renovated kitchen - island counter', '* Bay windows.', 'Hardwood floors.', 'Laundry in Building.', "* Food for thought near Tony's Pizzeria Napoletana, Original Joe's", "Trader Joe's, North Beach Restaurant and Victoria Bakery", '* Great Outdoors includes North Beach Park &;; Pool, Aquatic Park', 'and Washington Square.', 'Easy access to FiDi &;; DTSF.', '* Tails of the City pets BFF per owner approval.', 'Laundry in building', '* Utilities extra: tenants pay portion of electric, trash and water', '* Immediate occupancy.', 'No fee broker established 2004.', 'RentingSF', '#10886014']
